headline: American Homeowners Have More Extra Bedrooms Than Ever, New Realtor.com® Report Reveals
summary: Although your home might feel tight this holiday season, nationally, the number of extra bedrooms, defined as a bedroom that is in excess of the number of persons in the home, plus one to account for an office, has reached the highest levels in Census record history, according to a new report from Realtor.com® released today.
